<HEADLINE>
<P>
TIMES LAUNCHES VENTURA EDITION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Times today begins publication of a daily Ventura County Edition. 
</P>
<P>
Local news begins on page B1. A new weekly section called Ventura County Life 
will debut on Thursday. 
</P>
<P>
The edition will be produced by a staff in Ventura and printed at the Times 
Valley plant in Chatsworth. 
</P>
</TEXT>
