LOCKOUTS; TEAM OWNERS; COLLECTIVE BARGAINING; RADIO INDUSTRY -- LOS ANGELES; 
RADIO PROGRAMS; RADIO STATIONS; TALK SHOWS; KING, LARRY; OLDEN, PAUL; BIELER, 
ED (SUPERFAN); KFI (RADIO STATION); KABC (RADIO STATION); KMPC (RADIO STATION) 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
