IRVINE (CA) -- PUBLIC FACILITIES; LIABILITY; LEADERSHIP; ART EXHIBITS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA031290-0100 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 188523 </DOCID>
<DATE>
