ANGELES COUNTY; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- SUITS; LOS ANGELES COUNTY BOARD OF 
SUPERVISORS; SCHARBARUM, PETE; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- POLITICS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
