OFFICIALS; CALIFORNIA -- POLITICS; GUN CONTROL; POLITICAL ACTIVISM; ABORTION; 
LIBERALS; POLITICAL CANDIDATES; CALIFORNIA -- ELECTIONS -- 1990 
</P>
