<DATELINE>
<P>
DUBAI, United Arab Emirates 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The United Arab Emirates soccer team, one of the finalists for the World Cup, 
today announced the resignation of national Coach Bernard Blaut. 
</P>
<P>
Blaut, appointed in January after Brazilian Mario Zagalo was fired, resigned 
because of his handling of the team at the 10th Gulf Cup competition, in which 
the team finished last. 
</P>
