STUDENTS; HONORS; CAREERS; BLACKS -- UNITED STATES; UNITED STATES -- EDUCATION; 
HARVARD UNIVERSITY; EDITORS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA031290-0145 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 279223 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
March 12, 1990, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<P>
MITCHEL BANG 
</P>
<SECTION>
<P>
